      • FastaRecord

        public FastaRecord(java.lang.String header,
                   java.lang.String sequence,
                   java.lang.String customLetters)
        For gathering data on one FASTA record (header followed by sequence). Sets all variables.
        Parameters:
        header - raw FASTA header from file - should still start with '>'
        sequence - raw FASTA sequence from file - may contain newline characters
        customLetters - a string containing a set of custom AA letters. Only [A-Z] allowed
